statements: SELECT * FROM quantum_sensor_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;

SELECT event_id, sensor_id, event_type, event_description FROM SensorEvents WHERE event_type = 'Calibration' OR event_type = 'Maintenance' ORDER BY event_timestamp DESC;

SELECT s.sensor_id, s.sensor_name, c.calibration_value, m.maintenance_description FROM QuantumSensorData s LEFT JOIN SensorCalibration c ON s.sensor_id = c.sensor_id LEFT JOIN SensorMaintenance m ON s.sensor_id = m.sensor_id WHERE c.calibration_value > 10 AND m.maintenance_date > '2022-01-01';
